<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.3">
<l>tūvāya puḷḷūrntu vantu tuṟaivēḻam</l>
<l>mūvāmai nalki mutalai tuṇittāṉai</l>
<l>tēvāti tēvaṉaic ceṅkamalak kaṇṇāṉai</l>
<l>nāvāyu ḷāṉai naṟaiyūril kaṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw in Naṟaiyūr the one who, riding a divine bird,</l>
<l>Coming to the banks, favoring an elephant so that it is not ruined,</l>
<l>Cut down a crocodile, the primal god of gods,</l>
<l>The one with eyes like rosy lotuses, the one who is [always] on my tongue.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
